 Lady Gaga表示新专辑将充满“不同的流派、不同的风格、不同的梦想” https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-says-new-album-will-be-full-of- Different-genres- Different-styles- Different-dreams-3823903?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=lady-gaga-说新专辑将充满不同流派、不同风格、不同梦想Surej SinghFri, 20 Dec 2024 02:02:38 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3823903 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/lady-gaga@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/lady-gaga@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/lady-gaga@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/lady-gaga@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/lady-gaga@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/lady-gaga@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/lady-gaga@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “它以一种近乎腐败的方式跨越流派”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-says-new-album-will-be-full-of-different-genres-different-styles-different-dreams-3823903">Lady Gaga 称新专辑将充满“不同流派、不同风格、不同梦想”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/lady-gaga@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/lady-gaga@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/lady-gaga@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/lady-gaga@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/lady-gaga@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/lady-gaga@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/lady-gaga@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>透露了有关她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-hints-lead-single-from-next-album-arriving-october-3790256">即将发行的第七张专辑的</a>新细节——请参阅下面她所说的内容。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/joker-folie-a-deux-review-lady-gaga-3790522"><b>《小丑：Folie à Deux》评论：Lady Gaga 在一部挑衅性的监狱音乐剧中大放异彩</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>十月，这位“Born This Way”歌手分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-lady-gaga-dramatic-new-single-disease-3806194">引人注目的新流行单曲“Disease”</a> ，这是她新专辑的主打单曲。尽管这张唱片被歌迷称为“LG7”并预计将于明年二月上市，但人们对这张唱片知之甚少。</p><p>这首歌见证了 Lady Gaga 重返流行乐坛，在此之前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lady-gaga-and-bruno-mars-70s-country-themed-die-with-a-smile-music-video-3784255">Bruno Mars 于 8 月与布鲁诺·马尔斯 (Bruno Mars) 合作创作了力量民谣《Die With A Smile》</a> 。</p><p>现在，Gaga 在<a href="https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/music/story/2024-12-19/lady-gaga-die-with-a-smile-bruno-mars-grammys-coachella-interview">接受《<em>洛杉矶时报》的</em>新采访</a>时透露了有关“LG7”的更多信息。在谈到新唱片时，她表示，就像主打单曲之间的并置一样，这张专辑将探索“如此多不同的流派、如此多不同的风格、如此多不同的梦想”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3823825" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3823825" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3823825" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lady-Gaga@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Lady Gaga 于 2017 年在 Coachella 舞台上表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lady-Gaga@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lady-Gaga@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lady-Gaga@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lady-Gaga@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lady-Gaga@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lady-Gaga@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3823825" class="wp-caption-text"> Lady Gaga 于 2017 年在科切拉音乐节舞台上表演。图片来源：Christopher Polk/Getty Images for Coachella</figcaption></figure><p>她继续解释道：“它以一种近乎腐败的方式跨越了流派。并以爱结束。这就是我生命中所有混乱的答案，那就是我在爱中找到了平静。我写的每一首歌，都让我沉浸在关于过去的不同梦境中——几乎就像是回忆起我一生中做出的所有错误决定。但最终还是在这个非常幸福的地方结束。”</p><p>在聊天的其他地方，她说《Die With A Smile》是《LG7》的“重要组成部分”，将其比作“这个缺失的部分”。她还开玩笑说，她已经开始制作该唱片的视觉表现形式，并将在她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2025-lady-gaga-green-day-post-malone-travis-scott-lead-line-up-3814558">2025 年 Coachella 音乐节的头条节目</a>中展示。</p><p>回顾 2017 年碧昂斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-cancels-coachella-2017-headline-2018-1988314">因怀孕而不得不退出</a>后，Gaga 临时决定的头条新闻，她说：“我没有时间完全做我真正想做的事情……我做到了，而且我喜欢它。但你知道当你心中有一个关于你想要如何做某事的愿景时吗？是时候实现它了。”</p><p>在解释歌迷对即将发行的 LP 的期望时，她本月早些时候表示，《Disease》感觉像是“<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-talks-true-chaos-of-new-album-3820703">进入专辑混乱的一种方式</a>，这是一种混乱中的练习——我作为一个人的不同侧面”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3823826" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3823826" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3823826" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lady-Gaga-2017@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Lady Gaga 于 2017 年在科切拉舞台上表演。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lady-Gaga-2017@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lady-Gaga-2017@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lady-Gaga-2017@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lady-Gaga-2017@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lady-Gaga-2017@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lady-Gaga-2017@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3823826" class="wp-caption-text"> Lady Gaga 于 2017 年在科切拉音乐节舞台上表演。图片来源：Christopher Polk/Getty Images for Coachella</figcaption></figure><p>在《Disease》之前，Gaga 分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-announces-joker-2-companion-album-harlequin-3796692">《Harlequin》</a> ——她的电影 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/joker-folie-a-deux-review-lady-gaga-3790522"><em>《Joker: Folie à Deux》</em>的姊妹专辑。</a>这部电影虽然受到评论家的好评，但票房却惨败。 <em>《NME》</em>在对该片的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/joker-folie-a-deux-review-lady-gaga-3790522">四星级评论</a>中这样评价她的表演：“Lady Gaga 饰演的哈琳同样出色，与菲尼克斯之间产生了明显疯狂的化学反应，基纳和布莱丹·格里森都大力支持饰演杰基，一名监狱看守。对音乐剧的喜爱。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-says-new-album-will-be-full-of-different-genres-different-styles-different-dreams-3823903">Lady Gaga 称新专辑将充满“不同流派、不同风格、不同梦想”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
