pg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/live-charli-xcx-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/live-charli-xcx-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>宣布她和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/troye-sivan">Troye Sivan</a>将在“SWEAT PT”中重聚。明年，她将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/primavera-sound-festival">Primavera Sound</a>头条节目中出演《2》。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/charli-xcx-troye-sivan-sweat-tour-live-review-3796616">Charli XCX 和 Troye Sivan 住在纽约：前流行乐失败者巩固了他们作为竞技场杀手偶像的地位</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年早些时候，查莉（Charli）与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/CHAPPELL-ROAN">查普尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carptener">萨布丽娜·卡彭特（Sabrina Carpenter）</a>一起领衔《春》（Primavera），她称之为“神圣三位一体”——与西万（Sivan）一起开始了“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-and-troye-sivan-announce-charli-xcx-troye-sivan-present-sweat-north-american-arena-tour-3619000">SWEAT”美国巡演</a>，在多伦多、纽约、费城等主要城市停留、迈阿密、丹佛、洛杉矶等。</p><p>随后，为了支持她大获成功的第六张录音室专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">Brat</a> 》，她结束了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-charli-xcx-bring-out-robyn-caroline-polachek-and-yung-lean-in-london-for-brat-tour-3816973">在英国的个人巡演</a>，后来她告诉<em>《综艺》杂志，</em>大规模的演出“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-says-shes-often-in-a-lot-of-pain-when-performing-onstage-due-to-nerve-damage-in-neck-3819510">在情感上确实很困难</a>”，但她补充说，今年早些时候与 Sivan 一起巡演让她这种努力“对我来说容易得多，也少了一场情感斗争。” </p><figure id="attachment_3796693" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3796693" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3796693" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/charli-xcx-troye-sivan-sweat.jpg" alt="Charli XCX Troye Sivan Sweat 巡演" width="2000" height="1270" 